def is_chicken_pasta(pasta:item):
    # Function to check if the pasta is chicken pasta
    symbol is_chicken_pasta=exists food:item: is_food_chicken(food) and inside(food, pasta)
    return is_chicken_pasta

def is_plate_ready(plate:item, pasta:item):
    # Function to check if the plate is ready to receive the pasta
    symbol plate_ready=recipient(plate) and inside(pasta, plate)
    return plate_ready

behavior transfer_chicken_pasta(pasta:item, plate:item):

        achieve_once inhand(pasta)
